{"tid":96470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗青城肯認自己柒左未？","createTime":"2017-01-27T01:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T06:30:40.000Z","uid":38665,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"172597d25abf8736cc6b1e29972f121117b97d54","tid":96470,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%B4-%E8%8A%B1%E5%B8%82%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E7%9B%B8%E5%AE%89%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8B-%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259C%25AC%2F&d=uqPq7KTnenMUT4vIE0AL0UsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b8347ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258F%25B4-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259C%25AC%2F&h=d2641b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%B4-%E8%8A%B1%E5%B8%82%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C-%E7%9B%B8%E5%AE%89%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8B-%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E5%9B%9E%E6%9C%AC/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n情侶鄺振駹和吳麗英，於反水貨示威被捕，後者被控「以胸襲警」，舉世嘩然。雖上訴高院獲減刑，但罪名依然成立。兩人已申請上訴至終審法院，卻不獲法援。<br />\n<br />\n問：幾時開始計劃係花市擺檔？<br />\n<br />\n鄺：其實幾倉促，下定決心時，投標期已過一半。當時維園已經冇望，於是去沙田同荃灣搵位，最終揀左荃灣。<br />\n<br />\n問：你地已經提出上訴？<br />\n<br />\n鄺：已經交左申請，留待終審法院決定。最近收到通知，我地申請法援被拒，話理據不足。<br />\n<br />\n問：眾籌的目標係幾多？達唔達標？<br />\n<br />\n鄺：我地目標係 30 至 35 萬，之前網上呼籲已經籌到一半。而開檔到尋日啱啱回本，依幾日會繼續努力做生意。<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n問：一直擺檔都相安無事＊？<br />\n<br />\n（註：筆者在店外良久，見慕名而來的年輕人和姨姨一同揀衫，氣氛祥和）<br />\n<br />\n鄺：警民關係科特登嚟搵過我地，問我地政黨背景等等；便衣同食環都不時有人望住。但冇事發生。<br />\n<br />\n問：點解網上會爆發罵戰？<br />\n<br />\n鄺：啲衫係我同朋友一齊設計，對方係 designer，夾埋有五款 T-shirt，兩款衛衣。<br />\n<br />\n因為所有事都到最尾先決定。係我決定用「只有我們才是香港人」，但我事先唔知有類同嘅話出自陳雲先生。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地唔鍾意依個款，一來分開兩行唔好睇；二來電腦字唔型，想搵靚啲嘅書法。臨尾已經改左做「我係香港人」俾製衣廠，我手上仲有樣板。但到最後收貨，廠根本嚟唔切改，咁無辦法唯有照賣。<br />\n<br />\n問：最後問題比較敏感，你地有冇兼賣青政貨品？<br />\n<br />\n鄺：好老實，佢地需要嘅話，我地一定願意幫手。但暫時冇收過佢地要求同貨品，所以由開檔到而家都賣緊自己嘅貨。全部衫都係由我地設計，我地推出。"},{"pid":"257df8b50a823ea6762d6088cfa50fd240865d22","tid":96470,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"look7s個page仲屌緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f97cf03d40d2c3ff65578365205dfc3dd605af","tid":96470,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"呢班生蕃真係無賴到極置"},{"pid":"0ecca07158c3567c4c4770eb92b44b243e4b802d","tid":96470,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"原來佢地讀恆管？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f9e02569b83542795496e05c8beaa6610da435","tid":96470,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"Cowsep : 屌你老母 on9"},{"pid":"5c0f29ee4175dcd0714c0b2c0cd314a68b951b89","tid":96470,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:58:24.000Z","msg":"Lm見證佢地下屆/下下屆/n屆 選舉慘敗收場<br />\n永遠一事無成"},{"pid":"9b35b4dea039565dfe910e3a76e55d7b891f38e2","tid":96470,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢班生蕃真係無賴到極置</blockquote><br />\n死不認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218ba07559e8c7cc0398cfab940163e3700a71a0","tid":96470,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"見到高登班信徒仲死撐就火滾，<br />\n成班垃圾連義士都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ec8f27ed4f945ffadef035156e24a6342452c2","tid":96470,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢班生蕃真係無賴到極置</blockquote><br />\n死不認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要認錯,你幾時會見宗教(邪教)係會認錯架?"},{"pid":"984a3f1212097cab608079b4a1cbc1e26ff6011d","tid":96470,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"死唔認錯<br />\n<br />\n話你檔野係青政&gt;個負責人係本民青人&gt;佢喺channel-i主持&gt;總之本民青人share就唔得！<br />\n<br />\n點都可以由得佢地spin<br />\n算啦 點都好 佢地今次的確曲線宣傳左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}